OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,FBroadcast regulator Ofcom has upheld
OL,7,Fpart of a complaint by the police
OL,8,Fwatchdog over an episode of Panorama
OL,9,Fabout the shooting of gang member
OL,10,FChris Kaba.
OL,12,FThe documentary included claims by
OL,13,Fformer regional director Sal Naseem
OL,14,Fwho suggested that a murder
OL,15,Finvestigation into the police officer
OL,16,Fwho shot Mr Kaba was launched amid
OL,17,Fpressure over potential public
OL,18,Fdisorder.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC), which denied the
OL,8,Fclaim, objected after its statement
OL,9,Fwas not included in the initial
OL,10,Fbroadcast of the programme, and the
OL,11,FBBC refused to make a public apology.
OL,13,FGang member Mr Kaba was shot by police
OL,14,Fofficer Martyn Blake after trying to
OL,15,Fram his way past police cars in
OL,16,FStreatham, south-east London, in
OL,17,FSeptember 2022.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,FMr Blake was cleared in October after
OL,7,Fan Old Bailey trial, with questions
OL,8,Fraised over whether he should ever
OL,9,Fhave faced prosecution, and is waiting
OL,10,Fto learn whether he will have to face
OL,11,Fdisciplinary proceedings.
OL,13,FIn its findings, published on Monday,
OL,14,FOfcom said that the programme makers
OL,15,Fdid not give the IOPC a proper chance
OL,16,Fto respond to criticisms by former
OL,17,FMetropolitan Police Assistant
OL,18,FCommissioner Neil Basu, and former
OL,19,Farmed officer Tony Long.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,FThe IOPC launched a homicide
OL,7,Finvestigation four days after Mr Kaba
OL,8,Fwas shot.
OL,10,FMr Basu told the programme: "To come
OL,11,Fout so early in an investigation and
OL,12,Fannounce that they are looking at it
OL,13,Fas a potential murder investigation,
OL,14,Fit seems remarkable that that happened
OL,15,Fso quickly.
OL,26,@rD@]OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,F"You can't call it homicide until
OL,7,Fyou've gathered all of the evidence,
OL,8,Fbut I think in the early stages of
OL,9,Fthat investigation, they were making a
OL,10,Ffront page news announcement for a
OL,11,Fpurpose."
OL,13,FFormer firearms officer Tony Long, who
OL,14,Fwas himself acquitted of the murder of
OL,15,Frobbery suspect Azelle Rodney in 2005,
OL,16,Fsaid: "My personal feeling is that the
OL,17,FIOPC is absolutely obsessed with
OL,18,Fproving their worth, and I just
OL,19,Fgenuinely think that they will not be
OL,20,Fhappy until they've got a successful
OL,21,Fprosecution".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]xD@GOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,FThe watchdog said it decided to
OL,7,Fcriminally investigate Sergeant Blake,
OL,8,Fand later refer the case to the Crown
OL,9,FProsecution Service for a charging
OL,10,Fdecision, only after "careful
OL,11,Fconsideration of a significant amount
OL,12,Fof evidence gathered during our
OL,13,Findependent investigation and by
OL,14,Fapplying the relevant legal tests
OL,15,Fwhich govern our work."
OL,26,@rD@VOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,FOfcom's report said: "In relation to
OL,7,FMr Naseem's contribution, Ofcom found
OL,8,Fthat the broadcaster took reasonable
OL,9,Fcare to satisfy itself that material
OL,10,Ffacts were not presented, disregarded
OL,11,For omitted in the programme in a way
OL,12,Fthat resulted in unfairness to the
OL,13,FIOPC.
OL,15,F"However, in relation to the
OL,16,Fcriticisms made by Mr Basu and Mr
OL,17,FLong, we considered that these
OL,18,Fcomments had the potential to
OL,19,Fmaterially or adversely affect
OL,20,Fviewers' opinions of the IOPC in a way
OL,21,Fthat was unfair.
OL,26,@nD@VOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,F"We also considered that the
OL,7,Fbroadcaster was required, given the
OL,8,Fparticular circumstances of this case,
OL,9,Fto have given the IOPC an appropriate
OL,10,Fand timely opportunity to respond
OL,11,Fprior to the programme being broadcast
OL,12,Fand made available on BBC iPlayer, but
OL,13,Fthat it failed to do so.
OL,15,F"We also considered that the omission
OL,16,Fof the IOPC's statement in the
OL,17,Fprogramme resulted in unfairness to
OL,18,Fthe IOPC."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,FThe BBC had argued that Mr Basu and Mr
OL,7,FLong's comments were presented as
OL,8,Ftheir personal and professional
OL,9,Fopinions.
OL,11,FIOPC director-general Rachel Watson
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are pleased that Ofcom has
OL,13,Fupheld two of our complaints in
OL,14,Frelation to the BBC's Panorama
OL,15,Fprogramme about the fatal shooting of
OL,16,FChris Kaba, broadcast in November 2024.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,F"It agreed that the IOPC was treated
OL,7,Funfairly by the BBC when we were given
OL,8,Fno right to reply to damaging
OL,9,Fcriticisms made about us within that
OL,10,Fprogramme and for not including a
OL,11,Fstatement we provided prior to its
OL,12,Fbroadcast.
OL,14,F"Those criticisms were deeply
OL,15,Fconcerning given they directly
OL,16,Fquestioned our independence and
OL,17,Fdecision-making.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,F"We felt we had no choice but to
OL,7,Fescalate our complaints to Ofcom after
OL,8,Fexhausting the BBC's complaint
OL,9,Fprocedures.
OL,11,F"While the BBC eventually admitted it
OL,12,Fhad breached its own editorial
OL,13,Fstandards, it refused to make a public
OL,14,Fapology, despite the IOPC providing
OL,15,Fevidence to show the serious
OL,16,Freputational damage caused to our
OL,17,Forganisation as a result of the
OL,18,Fprogramme.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,F"While the damage caused by the
OL,7,Fdocumentary cannot be undone, we
OL,8,Fwelcome Ofcom's ruling that the IOPC
OL,9,Fwas treated unfairly and are pleased
OL,10,Fthat the BBC has been held to account."
OL,12,FA BBC spokesperson said: "We note the
OL,13,Ffindings of this Ofcom ruling, which
OL,14,Fare broadly in line with the
OL,15,Fconclusions reached by the BBC's
OL,16,FExecutive Complaints Unit in dealing
OL,17,Fwith the IOPC's initial complaint.
OL,19,F"We are pleased that the complaint
OL,20,Frelating to Mr Naseem's contribution
OL,21,Fwas not upheld.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@gO]tD@ZOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
