PN,40713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778677871
OL,3,CWatchdog complaint over Chris Kaba
OL,4,CPanorama documentary partly upheld
OL,6,F"We took quick action to add the
OL,7,Fstatement made by the IOPC after the
OL,8,Fcriminal trial to the iPlayer version
OL,9,Fof the programme, and to the online
OL,10,Farticle.
OL,12,F"We always strive to be as fair and
OL,13,Fthorough as possible when offering and
OL,14,Fincluding responses from people and
OL,15,Forganisations in our programmes."
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@aO]
